# {{ project_name }}

## Project Structure

This is a uv workspace monorepo.

- `apps/` — Application packages
- `packages/` — Shared libraries (added as needed)

## Commands

All commands are run via `just` from the project root:

- `just start` — Start Postgres + API dev server (clean exit on Ctrl+C)
- `just test` — Run all tests
- `just lint` — Lint with Ruff
- `just format` — Format with Ruff
- `just db-migrate` — Apply database migrations
- `just db-revision "description"` — Create a new migration

## Development

1. `uv sync` — Install dependencies
2. `just db-migrate` — Apply migrations
3. `just start` — Start Postgres + dev server

## Conventions

- Python type hints on all function signatures
- Ruff for linting and formatting (not flake8/black/isort)
- SQLModel for database models (combines SQLAlchemy + Pydantic)
- Alembic for database migrations
- pytest for testing with httpx for API tests
- All packages use uv workspace references
